text:
We used to see gibberish when a print driver was not quite right for the given
printer model. 
It’s been a very long time since I’ve had to deal with this one so I can’t
remember but it seems to me that there’s memory of HP shoehorning a driver into
Windows that then didn’t work quite right with an older printer. 
Philip Elder MCTS 
Senior Technical Architect 
Microsoft High Availability MVP
